  "title": "Repair Technician | Gross up to $3,200/month|Woodlands  -lq",
  "description": "<p>Location: North West (Woodlands MRT)<br />Salary Package: Gross up to $3k/month </p><p>Working days: Mon - Fri, Office hours </p><p>Key Duties: </p><ul><li>Perform repair, refurbishment, and testing of equipment parts and components</li><li>Troubleshoot and resolve electrical and mechanical faults</li><li>Maintain workbench tools, spare parts, and repair records accurately</li><li>Ensure all repairs meet performance and quality standards before returning to production</li><li>Work closely with engineering teams to improve equipment reliability and reduce downtime</li><li>Follow safety, ESD, and cleanroom procedures at all times</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Min Nitec in <strong>Electronics, Mechatronics, or Electrical Engineering</strong> (or related field)</li><li>At least 1 year of relevant experience in equipment repair or precision system maintenance (Semiconductor experience preferred)</li><li>Proficient with diagnostic tools (e.g., multimeter, oscilloscope) and mechanical hand tools</li><li>Comfortable to work in a cleanroom environment</li></ul><p>Please submit your updated resume on Whatsapp at wa.me/6587504643 or press the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p><br /></p><p>By submitting your resume and/or personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal data by the company (or its designated agent) for the purposes of processing, administration and managing your job application.</p><p><br /></p><p>Please be notified that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p>Charlotte Loh| Reg No.: R25127073</p><p>Griffin HR Consultancy Pte Ltd | EA Licence No.: 23C1449</p><p><br /></p>",
